OpenNI2
make ALLOW_WARNINGS=1

In /usr/local/include:
ln -s ~/src/OpenNI2/Include ./OpenNI2
ln -s ~/src/NiTE-MacOSX-x64-2.2/Include ./NiTE

In /usr/local/lib:
ln -s ~/src/OpenNI2/Bin/x64-Release/lib* .
ln -s ~/src/OpenNI2/Bin/x64-Release/OpenNI2 .
ln -s ~/src/NiTE-MacOSX-x64-2.2/Redist/libNiTE2.* .
ln -s ~/src/NiTE-MacOSX-x64-2.2/Redist/NiTE2 .

You must put the ini file with the .so file in the same directory wherever you go
